## ğŸ“Š Algorithm Flow (Simplified)

```mermaid
graph TD
A[User opens feed] --> B[Fetch recent posts from followed users]
B --> C[Calculate engagement score]
C --> D[Analyze hashtag relevance & AI tags]
D --> E[Rank posts based on interest]
E --> F[Display top-N results in feed]
````

